data.description: Nestled at the foothills of the Sacramento mountain, this home offers a picturesque escape with breathtaking views. Imagine waking up to the sun rising in your backyard over the mountain or enjoying a cup of coffee while surrounded by the beauty of New Mexico. Step inside to discover vaulted ceilings, wood beam accents, a brick fireplace, and cool gray tones which create a cozy atmosphere. The kitchen boasts an inviting space with an eat in kitchen with bay window, complemented by a traditional farmhouse barn door. Featuring three bedrooms, two bathrooms, two car garage, and a separate laundry room, this home is designed for your convenience.  Embrace the charm and make this your dream retreat!  Check out the 3D tour today!
